title: Unemployment rate in Cambodia 2019
summary: Overall Unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
Unemployment rate is slightly decreasing from 2006 to 2007, roughly constant from 2007 to 2008, slightly increasing from 2008 to 2009, and finally roughly decreasing from 2009 to 2011.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 1.38 was reported at Year 2010
The lowest Unemployment rate, of value 1.15 was reported at Year 2008
min_summary: In general Unemployment rate has stayed the same over the Year.
Unemployment rate is slightly decreasing from 2006 to 2007, roughly constant from 2007 to 2008, slightly increasing from 2008 to 2009, and finally roughly decreasing from 2009 to 2011.
